author: Kyle Olson, Kyle Olson
title: Michigan Attorney General Urges Residents to Call Cops on Neighbors Violating Stay-at-Home Order
description: Michigan Attorney General Dana Nessel is asking residents to tattle on their neighbors if they believe they are violating the governor's stay-at-home order.
content:
Michigan Attorney General Dana Nessel is asking residents to tattle on their neighbors if they believe they are violating the governor’s stay-at-home order.
